UE5 Blueprint File - BP_NPC_Base_v01
========================================

This is a Blueprint Class that extends ANPC_Base (C++ class).

To create this blueprint in Unreal Engine 5.2+:
1. Right-click in Content Browser
2. Search for "ANPC_Base"
3. Select "BP_NPC_Base_v01"
4. Click "Create"

Components:
- CharacterMesh (SkeletalMeshComponent)
- DialogueComponent (UDialogueComponent)
- QuestComponent (UQuestComponent)
- BehaviorTreeComponent (UBehaviorTreeComponent)
- BlackboardComponent (UBlackboardComponent)
- AIController (AIController)
- CapsuleComponent (Collision)
- SceneComponent (Root)

Variables:
- NPCName (String)
- NPCRole (Enum: Citizen, Student, Vendor, Police, GangMember, Government, CircleAgent, FamilyMember)
- NPCDistrict (Enum: Riverside, Kumasi, CapeCoast, NewAccra, Tamale, CircleFoundation)
- CurrentState (Enum: Idle, Walking, Working, Sleeping, Dialogue, Combat, Fleeing, Questing)
- IsKeyNPC (Boolean)
- IsPersistent (Boolean)
- HomeLocation (Vector)
- HomeRotation (Rotator)
- Reputation (Float)
- InteractionCooldown (Float)

Events:
- BeginPlay()
- Tick(float DeltaTime)
- OnConstruction(const FTransform& Transform)
- Destroyed()

Functions:
- SetNPCRole(ENPCRole)
- SetNPCDistrict(ENPCDistrict)
- SetState(ENPCState)
- GetHomeLocation() -> Vector
- SetHomeLocation(Vector)
- IsAvailableForInteraction() -> Boolean
- OnPlayerProximity(ACharacter*)
- OnPlayerFar()
- OnDamage(float, AActor*)
- OnDeath()
- OnQuestComplete(FString)
- GetReputation() -> Float
- AddReputation(float)
- RemoveReputation(float)
- GetCurrentState() -> ENPCState
- GetNPCRole() -> ENPCRole
- GetNPCDistrict() -> ENPCDistrict
- GetNPCName() -> String

Note: This blueprint must be compiled after adding components.
Note: This blueprint requires meshes from 3D artists.
Note: This blueprint requires animations from animators.